name: For Clarina
description:
This music is for Clarina (NFTipi)
In the NFT world it is easy to find wonderful people, it is easy to get collaborations with artists, it is easy to discover inspiration through the art of many.
In this virtual world everything is fast and blockchains leave our work secure, encrypted forever, profits run or marketing stagnates from one moment to the next.
All of us here are learning, discovering how much and how ...
Among all this world there is an angel who takes the best struggles and justice to make it his; he unites the communities and takes out the best of them to distribute ... that is Clarina or NFTipi.
I have heard and read a lot about her, she has given me her smile, her affection and her encouragement. It is one of those luck that knocks on your door one day and remains despite the distance and all the difficulties.
Clarina is a bridge between people to connect souls. Clarina is light, patience, pride and her healthy voice.
Beyond the ego, beyond the pains, as a hope in humanity all is NFTipi.
This music is a small gift for the enormous work of Clarina ...
With all the love in the universe, For Clarina.
